description: Another guy from a small town. To be honest, I can't get enough of them. Always so full of optimism and ideas. They're easy prey, that's why I love them. This one was a carpenter without any actual experience in the trade. Instead he worked here and there after school, his life was going nowhere. He decided to move to Prague and start new. In his case, price of a new life was 5 000 Crowns for our mediation fee. It was too much for the boy so he had to make a difficult choice. Undress or go home empty handed. Of course he undressed, I just had to promise not to show the video to his girlfriend. She won't be happy to see what her sweetie was willing to do for money. He was a really greedy boy. I fucked him like a little bitch but he didn't mind it that much.
title: Dirty Scout 167
